      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Alberto Sanjuan</b>\n</p><p><b>Alberto Sanjuan</b>,<br />\na Spanish computer engineer and computer chess programmer living in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seville\">Seville</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andalusia\">Andalusia</a>. \nSupported by chess advisers <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose_Antonio_Morillas&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jose Antonio Morillas (page does not exist)\">Jose Antonio Morillas</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Juan_Jos%C3%A9_Corbal%C3%A1n&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Juan José Corbalán (page does not exist)\">Juan José Corbalán</a>, Alberto Sanjuan is primary author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/Rhetoric\" title=\"Rhetoric\">Rhetoric</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alberto_Sanjuan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alberto_Sanjuan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40283\">question about SEE</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 05, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41541\">Ponder 'on' in LittleBlitzer</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2011 &#160;» <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a>, <a href=\"/LittleBlitzer\" title=\"LittleBlitzer\">LittleBlitzer</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42291\">Moving to Magic Bitboards... any advice?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43144\">New engine: Rhetoric</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 03, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47564\">Root move order (again)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 21, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48418\">Rhetoric 1.0, new version</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 25, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48823\">passed pawn question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 02, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Passed_Pawn\" title=\"Passed Pawn\">Passed Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50430\">Hash tables: one bound or two bounds?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 11, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51847\">Endgame tablebase generation for newbies</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 04, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54241\">Solving a fail low situation at the root</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 03, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Low\" title=\"Fail-Low\">Fail-Low</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alberto_Sanjuan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58376\">Rhetoric 1.4.3 Released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 26, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=65484\">AlphaGo Zero</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 19, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=AlphaGo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"AlphaGo (page does not exist)\">AlphaGo</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68655&amp;start=2\">Re: A genetic chess engine?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2018 </li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68655&amp;start=6\">Re: A genetic chess engine?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Alberto Sanjuan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 18, 2018</dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alberto_Sanjuan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180820102052/http://www.chessrhetoric.com/\">Rhetoric, un nuevo estil</a> (Spanish, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, August 20, 2018)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alberto_Sanjuan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20180823125714/http://www.chessrhetoric.com/index.php/equipo\">Rhetoric - Equipo de Desarrollo</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, August 23, 2018</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301151544\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 37/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 74/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7379-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301151544 and revision id 20791\n -->\n"
